data.description: Come and take a look at this amazing opportunity! This gorgeous home offers much to be desired, as well as versatility and space, with 4 oversized bedrooms with walk-in closets, and a loft! Upgraded flooring downstairs as well as kitchen countertops. The solar allows for an unimaginably low electric bill throughout the year! The home is conveniently placed close to much shopping, dining, etc! Please come and take a look today!
